InstancePopulator - Class in com.github.ozcanturkmen.ontocsv
InstancePopulator class provides the methods to populate an OWL ontology (in RDF/XML format) with instances provided via a CSV (comma separated values) file.
InstancePopulator.Builder - Class in com.github.ozcanturkmen.ontocsv
Static inner class which is used to create InstancePopulator instances in compliance with the Builder design pattern.
InstancePopulator.Configurator - Class in com.github.ozcanturkmen.ontocsv
Static inner class used by Jackson ObjectMapper during deserialization of the key-value pairs found within the transformations configuration file (YAML).
InstancePopulator.Configurator.Transformation - Class in com.github.ozcanturkmen.ontocsv
Static inner class encapsulating the pattern and replacement parameters for a transformation consisting of a String.replaceAll(String, String) operation.
